export interface IUser{
    id: number,
    role: string,
    name: string,
    lastName: string,
    quote: string,
    birthday: string,
    nativeCity: string,
    email: string, 
    status: string,
    freinds: any
}

export class User implements IUser{
    id = -1
    role = null,
    name: string,
    lastName: string,
    quote: string,
    birthday: string,
    nativeCity: string,
    email: string, 
    status: string,
    freinds: any
}
